name: Desjardins Canadian Preferred Share Index ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of a broad Canadian bond index. The investment strategy of the ETF is to invest, directly or indirectly, in a portfolio of Canadian fixed income securities that closely matches the Index. The Index is composed of Canadian investment-grade fixed income securities issued in the Canadian market, including government, quasi-government and corporate bonds.
